    "descriptionHtml": "the jordan 1 low sepatent elephant black (women's) is a sophisticated, high-fashion sneaker for fun and dressy wear.  it is all-black, made of high-quality leather, and accented with a patterned and textured patent leather material for an elegant touch.\n<br>\n<br>\nof course, the shoe is made extra special with various nike and jordan logos, such as the jordan flight logo on the outer tongue and the swoosh symbol on the side of the shoe. perforations on the toe cap and sides give this sneaker enhanced breathability, and nike air technology provides the shoe with extra cushioning for better comfort and support throughout the day.\n<br>\n<br>\nthe jordan 1 low sepatent elephant black (women's) is a laced sneaker with black laces for a classic sneaker look. our team is most impressed with the placement of the white wings air jordan logo on the shoe's heel. nike released this shoe on july 1, 2024. it originally retailed for $125.",
